<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>BlackHorse Property Care — Business Card</title>
<style>
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 20px;
  background: #f5f5f5;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
}

/* BUSINESS CARD — Staples standard 3.5" × 2" */
.card {
  width: 3.5in;
  height: 2in;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0f0d 0%, #111a15 100%);
  color: #f5f2eb;
  padding: 0.25in;
  margin: 20px auto;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: space-between;
  border-radius: 2px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* Subtle accent line */
.card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c8973a, #e0b86a, transparent);
}

/* TOP SECTION: Logo + Name */
.card-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.15in;
  padding-top: 0.05in;
}

.card-logo {
  width: 0.45in;
  height: 0.45in;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.card-logo svg {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.4));
}

.card-branding h1 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 0.55in;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 0.95;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: #e0b86a;
  margin: 0;
}

.card-branding p {
  font-size: 0.08in;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #4a9962;
  margin: 0.02in 0 0 0;
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* TAGLINE */
.card-tagline {
  font-size: 0.09in;
  font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(224, 184, 106, 0.85);
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  margin: 0.08in 0;
  font-weight: 300;
}

/* SERVICES */
.card-services {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 0.08in 0.15in;
  font-size: 0.065in;
  line-height: 1.3;
  color: rgba(245, 242, 235, 0.8);
  margin: 0.08in 0;
}

.card-services li {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.05in;
}

.card-services li::before {
  content: '✓';
  color: #c8973a;
  font-weight: 600;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: -0.01in;
}

/* BOTTOM SECTION: Contact + Locations */
.card-footer {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 0.1in;
  padding-top: 0.05in;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(224, 184, 106, 0.3);
}

.card-contact {
  flex: 1;
}

.card-contact-item {
  font-size: 0.07in;
  line-height: 1.2;
  color: #f5f2eb;
  margin: 0.02in 0;
}

.card-contact-label {
  font-size: 0.055in;
  color: #4a9962;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.card-contact-value {
  font-size: 0.076in;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: #e0b86a;
}

.card-web {
  font-size: 0.065in;
  color: rgba(245, 242, 235, 0.75);
}

.card-areas {
  font-size: 0.06in;
  color: rgba(245, 242, 235, 0.6);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

/* QR CODE — Small, bottom right */
.card-qr {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0.12in;
  right: 0.12in;
  width: 0.42in;
  height: 0.42in;
  background: #f5f2eb;
  padding: 0.04in;
  border-radius: 2px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.card-qr img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: contain;
}

/* PRINT STYLES */
@media print {
  body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: white; }
  .card { margin: 0; box-shadow: none; }
}

/* Preview / Instructions */
.instructions {
  max-width: 4in;
  margin: 40px auto;
  padding: 20px;
  background: white;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #333;
}

.instructions h2 {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: #0a0f0d;
}

.instructions ol {
  margin-left: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.instructions li {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.instructions strong {
  color: #c8973a;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
  <!-- Logo + Branding -->
  <div class="card-header">
    <div class="card-logo">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- Horse silhouette -->
        <path d="M25 55 Q20 50 18 40 Q16 30 20 25 Q25 20 30 22 Q32 18 38 15 L45 18 Q50 12 55 15 L60 10 Q65 8 68 15 Q72 12 76 18 L82 15 Q88 18 90 25 Q93 35 85 45 Q78 50 70 52 L65 55 Q60 70 45 75 Q30 75 25 60 Z M30 60 L32 75 M45 75 L45 85 M60 70 L58 82" 
              fill="none" stroke="#e0b86a" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="card-branding">
      <h1>BLACKHORSE</h1>
      <p>Property Care</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tagline -->
  <div class="card-tagline">We Show Up. We Deliver.</div>

  <!-- Services (2 columns) -->
  <ul class="card-services">
    <li>Lawn Mowing &amp; Edging</li>
    <li>Driveway Sealing</li>
    <li>Seasonal Cleanup</li>
    <li>Mulch Installation</li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Contact + Areas -->
  <div class="card-footer">
    <div class="card-contact">
      <div class="card-contact-item">
        <span class="card-contact-label">Call/Text</span><br>
        <span class="card-contact-value">(437) 219-6133</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-contact-item" style="margin-top: 0.06in;">
        <span class="card-web">blackhorsepropertycare.ca</span><br>
        <span class="card-areas">Milton • Oakville • Mississauga</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- QR Code (Instagram) -->
  <div class="card-qr">
    <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://www.instagram.com/blackhorsepropertycare" alt="Follow @blackhorsepropertycare">
  </div>
</div>

<div class="instructions">
  <h2>How to Print at Staples</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Save this as PDF:</strong> Print to PDF (Ctrl+P or Cmd+P) → Save as "BlackHorse-BusinessCard.pdf"</li>
    <li><strong>Upload to Staples Online:</strong> Go to staples.com → Print Services → Business Cards → Upload your PDF</li>
    <li><strong>Select options:</strong>
      <ul style="margin: 8px 0 8px 20px;">
        <li>Quantity: 500 or 1000</li>
        <li>Size: 3.5" × 2"</li>
        <li>Paper: Standard (Glossy looks sharper if budget allows)</li>
        <li>Copies per sheet: 10</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Review & Order:</strong> Proofread the preview, then order. Ready in 2-3 days, ~$30–$80 depending on quantity.</li>
  </ol>
  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-style: italic; color: #999;">
    💡 <strong>Tip:</strong> Print a test copy first at home to confirm sizing and colors before ordering 500+.
  </p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
